snippet.title: Coridden - Co-op Action RPG Announcement Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Become the creatures you defeat in this co-op action RPG! Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1656930/Coridden/
Chat with us! Join our discord: https://discord.gg/invite/fFdRsDW6Af
Or join our mailing list: https://coridden.com 

Coridden is developed by Aftnareld, a small indie studio from Sweden.
